snippet.textDisplay:
honestly, i think Oliver Tree is gonna kill his own persona, “Turbo”, and come back as someone else
he did this before with his old music career where he went by the name “Tree”.

the pink background could be a reference to pink guy, his joke music and the transition of george miller from filthy frank/pink guy to joji, making more serious music
plus, there’s a scene where Oliver grabs a doll that is similar to him and kicks it while saying “Somehow I’ve seen, You’ve turned into someone else”. he might be “kicking out” his persona from his musical career

he might also be killing his career. i think this is possible because at 1:04 he’s saying “You know I’ll never be back now”.

honestly, i’m fine with that. this dude can do whatever he wants, it’s his career. as long as he’s happy with his career, i’m happy.
